{
  "texts": [
    "However, GPT-4V outperformed in other metrics including a sensitivity of 0.86 compared to dermatologists' 0.71.",
    "A complete evaluation of this comparison is shown in Table 5.",
    "We encountered six parse errors (GPT-4V refused to answer that question).",
    "Among the remaining 612 questions, GPT-4V answers correctly for 361 questions, leading to an accuracy of 59.0%.",
    "Given this dataset was originally designed for open-ended answering, there is no baseline performance in terms of accuracy reported."
  ]
}